{"tid":1832430,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Zen 3 進展良好, AMD 已將代碼添加到 Linux 內核","createTime":"2020-01-21T07:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T00:03:53.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"aa9971bc02a3ff6e256a2095af25409f4380e548","tid":1832430,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:16:18.000Z","msg":"AMD CEO 蘇媽在 CES 2020 發布會後的 QA 問答中表示，我們能在2020年內看到 Zen 3，也就是說今年內 AMD 會發布基於 Zen 3 架構的處理器，確實從 AMD 的時間表上來看今年年末應該會發布新一代基於 Zen 3 架構的 Ryzen 處理器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.coolaler.com.tw/image/news/20/01/AMD-zen3_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F20%2F01%2FAMD-zen3_1.jpg&h=ec3f4277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在@KOMACHI_ENSAKA發現 Zen 3 的微代碼已經被添加到 Linux 內核中去了，新的 EDAC / amd64 新增了 AMD Family 19h 系列的支援，而現在 AMD 的 Zen 2 系列處理器是 Family 17h，新發布的 Ryzen 4000 系列移動處理器也被歸入到這一系列裡面，畢竟 Renoir APU 是基於 Zen 2 架構的。<br />\n<br />\n其實 Linux 內核中加入對 Zen 3 的支援也不能說明些什麼，畢竟系統怎麼都要提早對新處理器做好準備的，但這也可以當作 Zen 3 目前進度良好的證明。<br />\n<br />\n其實早在去年10月，AMD 在自己的YouTube頻道上公佈了一系列幻燈片，這是介紹基於 Zen 3 架構處理器的幻燈片，不過影片很快就被下線了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.coolaler.com.tw/image/news/20/01/AMD-zen3_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F20%2F01%2FAMD-zen3_2.jpg&h=62b04594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本在 Zen 2 上面，每個 CCD 上含有2個 CCX，一個 CCX 有4個 CPU 核心。而一個 CCD 上面的兩個 CCX 共享同樣的16MB L3 快取，所以一塊8核的 Zen 2 CPU 擁有32MB的，但它們是由分別位於兩個 CCX 中的16MB三級快取組合而成的。而在 Zen 3 上面，AMD 將原本的分離式 L3 快取改成了整個 CCD 共享同一塊 L3 快取。對於處理器來說，L3 是非常重要的，它甚至可以提供一些 IPC 提升，而 CCD 內共享 L3 可以使同一塊 CCD 上面的8個核心間數據交換的延遲減少，尤其是對於跨 CCX 的數據交換來說，這個提升會很明顯。<br />\n<br />\n另外可以看到，Zen 3 架構將仍然使用 MCM 封裝的形式，I/O 核心部分並沒有大改，而從路線圖上面還可以知道，此前傳聞中 AMD 正在研發的單核四線程技術並不會在 Zen 3 上面應用，而可能將會在 Genoa 或更後面的 CPU 上面使用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coolaler.com/threads/zen-3-amd-linux.358236/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com%2Fthreads%2Fzen-3-amd-linux.358236%2F&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6nXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=cfd8c3f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.coolaler.com/threads/zen-3-amd-linux.358236/</a>"},{"pid":"c76ca39cf6c851cfef146eb9ceac8c34a9169a1e","tid":1832430,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:37:56.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"750f6881d395101a8598e7b3e29a5850b5d56f52","tid":1832430,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:38:36.000Z","msg":"年末先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0585717784a8709dc8f1b08eeff9221019d38fa7","tid":1832430,"uid":242278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T12:25:08.000Z","msg":"對手連Zen2都打唔過就咁快岀Zen3<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0207fe53a219d03ef8e8d259ec3b94922fc4ff8","tid":1832430,"uid":134415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0585717784a8709dc8f1b08eeff9221019d38fa7","tid":1832430,"uid":242278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T12:25:08.000Z","msg":"對手連Zen2都打唔過就咁快岀Zen3<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T12:39:05.000Z","msg":"早前見過有消息話intel投誠搵tsmc代工7nm<br />\n係咪已經走投無路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2457cdae54f98af5f5f5974529c71cddb83b25f0","tid":1832430,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0207fe53a219d03ef8e8d259ec3b94922fc4ff8","tid":1832430,"uid":134415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0585717784a8709dc8f1b08eeff9221019d38fa7","tid":1832430,"uid":242278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T12:25:08.000Z","msg":"對手連Zen2都打唔過就咁快岀Zen3<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T12:39:05.000Z","msg":"早前見過有消息話intel投誠搵tsmc代工7nm<br />\n係咪已經走投無路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}